{"tid":1615772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急法係幫緊我地攬炒 搞機場都係想攬炒 依家仲要政府自投羅網 你地何需憂慮","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T08:19:49.000Z","uid":229436,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a2f244102ee63d07e5fb95d3e4fa01f8876852","tid":1615772,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:53:34.000Z","msg":"認真佢連緊急法都未必推到 何況蒙面法(立左都無人理啦 你去爆格會唔會因為怕比人告蒙面法而唔帶面具呀?)<br />\n<br />\n同埋即使佢出緊急法 我就真係唔驚 咩都無 爛命一條<br />\n最驚係香港D公司 同權貴仲有支那D走資有錢佬<br />\n因為緊急法係無限期進行 = 政府想抄你家就抄你家 唔需要有原因<br />\n你地成日講個D 咩江派習派 你地不如估下佢地會點仲好<br />\n<br />\n我就支持攬炒ga 緊急法立到你就快d立 唔好拖拉咁耐<br />\n我地搞機場都係想香港攬炒姐<br />\n緊急法簡直係完美推行攬炒<br />\n<br />\nBTW 我打賭林奠會連緊急法條鼻毛都店唔到  香港有d人唔會比佢過"},{"pid":"83527d53829e5d9d7ea07d5cb2d82c0c5f4d2393","tid":1615772,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b223d56a16db686b94f72b4b9332fb4748db2ed","tid":1615772,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a589bd7b330bcbdd348a337e9696d43e346e6d1","tid":1615772,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xTVdQ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xTVdQ5.jpg&h=a42c2f77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係就快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8521443ff9618789463986ffc0f35acd15525e3","tid":1615772,"uid":32108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:05:11.000Z","msg":"咁送中都係攬炒，係咪要支持？"},{"pid":"a286f83dd1b26f62cae5fd452c1ee82beac7eb00","tid":1615772,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,